## Architecture

### High-Level System Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Client["Browser (React + TypeScript + Vite)"]
        direction LR
        UI_Quiz["Quiz Flow UI<br/>Framer Motion transitions"]
        UI_Admin["Admin Panel<br/>Password-gated CRUD"]
        UI_Badge["Badge Screen<br/>Confetti + badge graphic"]
    end

    subgraph Supabase["Supabase (Serverless Backend)"]
        direction TB
        Auth["Supabase Auth<br/>Anonymous sign-in"]
        DB[("PostgreSQL<br/>questions · attempts · badges")]
        Storage["Supabase Storage<br/>badges bucket (public)"]
        Edge["Edge Function<br/>grade-attempt (Deno)"]
    end

    UI_Quiz -->|fetch questions| DB
    UI_Quiz -->|sign in anonymously| Auth
    UI_Quiz -->|save attempt| DB
    UI_Quiz -->|POST attemptId| Edge
    Edge -->|read questions + attempt| DB
    Edge -->|write badge record| DB
    Edge -->|returns passed / score| UI_Quiz
    UI_Badge -->|fetch badge image URL| Storage
    UI_Admin -->|CRUD questions| DB
```

