## System Design

### Three-Layer Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Presentation["Presentation Layer"]
        P1["Pages & Components<br/>React + Tailwind"]
        P2["Framer Motion<br/>Animated transitions"]
        P3["Canvas Confetti<br/>Badge celebration"]
    end

    subgraph Application["Application Layer"]
        A1["QuizContext<br/>useReducer state"]
        A2["Custom Hooks<br/>useQuestions · useTimer · useQuizSession"]
        A3["React Router v6<br/>Protected routes · useBlocker"]
    end

    subgraph Data["Data Layer"]
        D1["Services<br/>All Supabase calls isolated here"]
        D2["Types<br/>quiz.types.ts · zero any"]
        D3["Supabase Client<br/>anon key (browser safe)"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Serverless Backend"]
        B1["Supabase Auth<br/>Anonymous sessions"]
        B2["PostgreSQL + RLS<br/>Row-level security"]
        B3["Edge Function (Deno)<br/>grade-attempt · service-role key"]
        B4["Storage<br/>badges bucket · public CDN"]
    end

    Presentation <--> Application
    Application <--> Data
    Data <--> Backend
```

### Sequence: Full Quiz Run

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant React as React App
    participant Supabase as Supabase Auth + DB
    participant Edge as Edge Function

    User->>React: Visit /quiz
    React->>Supabase: signInAnonymously()
    Supabase-->>React: { user: { id: uuid } }

    React->>Supabase: SELECT * FROM questions ORDER BY order ASC
    Supabase-->>React: questions[]

    loop Per question
        React->>User: Show question (animated slide-in)
        Note over React: Timer starts (60s default)
        User->>React: Select answer + click Next
        React->>React: Record { questionId, selectedIndex, timeTaken }
        Note over React: Back navigation BLOCKED
    end

    React->>Supabase: INSERT INTO attempts (user_id, answers, started_at, completed_at)
    Supabase-->>React: { id: attemptId }

    React->>Edge: POST /grade-attempt { attemptId }
    Edge->>Supabase: Fetch attempt + questions (service-role key)
    Edge->>Edge: Compare selectedIndex vs correct_index for each answer

    alt All answers correct
        Edge->>Supabase: UPDATE attempts SET passed=true
        Edge->>Supabase: INSERT INTO badges (user_id, attempt_id, image_url)
        Edge-->>React: { passed: true, correct_count: N, total: N }
        React->>User: BadgeScreen + confetti 🎉
    else One or more wrong
        Edge-->>React: { passed: false, correct_count: N, total: N }
        React->>User: "Not quite — try again" screen
    end
```

