## User Flows

### Flow 1: Happy Path — Badge Unlocked

```mermaid
graph LR
    A([Visit /quiz]) --> B[Anonymous sign-in]
    B --> C[Start Screen]
    C --> D[Question 1]
    D --> E[Question 2 ...]
    E --> F[Final Question]
    F --> G[Attempt saved to Supabase]
    G --> H[grade-attempt Edge Function called]
    H --> I{All correct?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Badge written to DB]
    J --> K[🎉 Badge Screen + confetti]
    I -- No --> L[Try Again Screen]
```

### Flow 2: Timer Expiry

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Question displayed] --> B{Timer reaches 0}
    B --> C[Timeout recorded in answers jsonb]
    C --> D[Auto-advance to next question]
    D --> E[selected_index saved as -1]
```

### Flow 3: Admin — Adding a Question

```mermaid
graph LR
    A([Visit /admin]) --> B{Password correct?}
    B -- No --> C[Blocked — re-prompt]
    B -- Yes --> D[Admin dashboard]
    D --> E[Fill question form]
    E --> F[Set correct answer]
    F --> G[Set display order]
    G --> H[INSERT to questions table]
    H --> I[Question appears in list]
    I --> J{Edit or Delete?}
    J -- Edit --> E
    J -- Delete --> K[DELETE from questions table]
```

