## Metrics

| Metric | Value |
|---|---|
| Frontend framework | React 18 + TypeScript 5.9 |
| Build tool | Vite (< 2s cold build) |
| Animation library | Framer Motion |
| Backend | Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage + Edge) |
| Edge runtime | Deno (Supabase Edge Functions) |
| State management | React Context + useReducer |
| Code quality | SOLID principles, zero `any`, 150-line file limit |
| Security | RLS on all tables, service-role key server-side only |
| Monorepo tool | pnpm workspaces |

---

## Potential Enhancements

| Enhancement | Approach |
|---|---|
| Multiple badge tiers | Add `score_threshold` to a `badge_types` table |
| Leaderboard | Aggregate `attempts` with `passed=true`, rank by `time_taken` |
| Question categories | Add `category` column, filter per quiz session |
| Real admin auth | Replace password gate with Supabase email/password Auth |
| Retry cooldown | Store `last_attempt_at` and enforce cooldown in Edge Function |
| Analytics dashboard | Pipe `attempts` data to a Supabase view, display in admin |
| Offline support | PWA + IndexedDB for question caching |

